oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 6
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." This is part six of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is the twentieth of an unidentified number of tapes.
